text: Pyae Sone Naing (; born 3 July 2001) is a footballer from Myanmar, and a striker for Yadanarbon FC. He is the another product of Myanmar Football Academy. ==References== * pyae sone naing Category:Living people Category:Burmese footballers Category:2001 births Category:Association football forwards Category:Yadanarbon F.C. players
